### **🎯 TDG Quality Standards (ZERO TOLERANCE)**

**✅ COMPLIANCE REQUIREMENTS:**
- **100% Test Coverage**: ALL generated code must have corresponding tests
- **Test-First Evidence**: Documentation proving tests were written before code
- **Quality Validation**: Generated code must meet enterprise quality standards
- **TDG Methodology**: Complete adherence to Test-Driven Generation workflow
- **AI Agent Compliance**: ALL AI agents must follow TDG methodology

**❌ VIOLATION CATEGORIES (IMMEDIATE ACTION REQUIRED):**
- **Category 1**: Code generated without pre-existing tests (CRITICAL PRIORITY)
- **Category 2**: Tests written after code generation (HIGH PRIORITY)
- **Category 3**: Incomplete test coverage for generated code (MEDIUM PRIORITY)
