### **Required Compilation Commands (CLAUDE MUST USE)**

**🔧 MANDATORY Pattern for ALL Compilations:**
```bash
# ✅ CORRECT: Patient mode compilation with natural completion
export NO_TIMEOUT=true
export PATIENT_MODE=enabled
export INFINITE_PATIENCE=true
export BASH_DEFAULT_TIMEOUT_MS=3600000  # Override 2-minute default with 60 minutes
export BASH_MAX_TIMEOUT_MS=7200000      # Allow up to 2 hours if needed

# Then run compilation - it will complete naturally
mix compile --warnings-as-errors

# ❌ FORBIDDEN: Any artificial timeouts (CLAUDE MUST NEVER USE)
# bash -c "timeout 2m mix compile"       # CRITICAL VIOLATION - premature termination
# mix compile --timeout 120000            # CRITICAL VIOLATION - artificial limit
# Any command that interrupts compilation # CRITICAL VIOLATION - must run to completion
```

